# HCDE530 — project context for Cursor

## Directory structure (auto-generated)

Do not edit the fenced block between the HTML comments by hand. Refresh it after adding, renaming, or removing project files:

- **One-time setup (recommended):** from the repo root run `git config core.hooksPath .githooks` so each commit runs `tools/update_cursorrules_tree.py` and re-stages `.cursorrules`.
- **Any time:** run `python tools/update_cursorrules_tree.py` (or `py -3 tools/update_cursorrules_tree.py` on Windows) before pushing, or ask the agent to run it after file-tree changes.

The listing is derived from `git ls-files` (tracked + untracked, honoring `.gitignore`).

